START: Add Wazuh Webhook to Shuffle Workflow

1. Copy webhook URL
2. Go To Terminal
3. sudo nano /var/ossec/etc/ossec.conf
4. Insert Integration code as last entry within <ossec_config>

  <integration>
  <name>shuffle</name>
  <hook_url>YOUR_WEBHOOK_URL</hook_url>
  <level>3</level>
  <alert_format>json</alert_format>
  </integration>

Workflow Path:
  00_Wazuh_Webhook -> 01_Get_Set_Thread_TS (No Branch Conditional)
